    "settings.brackets_lede": "<strong>Progressive PIT brackets.</strong> Each bracket has: <em>Upper limit</em> (taxable income ≤ limit → applies this bracket), <em>Rate</em> (0.05 = 5%), <em>Subtractor</em> (the number subtracted in the short formula). Set <strong>Limit = 0</strong> for the top (open-ended) bracket. Formula: <code>Tax = Assessable income × Rate − Subtractor</code>",
